225
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] I svako toliko ti brnice stradave od udarca.

226
00:33:41,119 --> 00:33:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

227
00:33:41,759 --> 00:33:46,640
[SPEAKER_00] I to se mijenja i to su ljudi sretni ili nesretni itede Da malo skratim.

228
00:33:48,079 --> 00:33:49,039
